{"tid":777533,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"外母反對我同男朋友一齊結婚。。","createTime":"2018-08-13T03:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T05:11:34.000Z","uid":158407,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b9bbe9acdf4c69162c4a494336958ed2705f0db6","tid":777533,"uid":158407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:43:34.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊左六年以上，中五已經一齊左，最近諗住同男朋友移民澳洲結婚，同左未來外母食左餐飯同佢講晒我地結婚計劃，因為已經儲左筆錢諗住係個邊開餐廳。點知外母極力反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又話咩點解要搬去咁遠，又話咩我地個時中學讀慈幻已經覺得我好無禮貌，一直都唔想我同佢一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成餐飯食得勁唔開心面阻阻咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想問下巴打係咪真係無機會。。"},{"pid":"abb413e4f5e49d97f4004687d0c1cc680fce4bef","tid":777533,"uid":34571,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:45:25.000Z","msg":"慈幼， 有無新意"},{"pid":"5e80f1530bea817609d681563ae0a336b7d06693","tid":777533,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:45:56.000Z","msg":"so low"},{"pid":"61038f1b01253f4b034e9093218e15f713c51bda","tid":777533,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:46:41.000Z","msg":"this is so great"},{"pid":"dd631b8a33bc364fad518dd424d87034a8fbffa4","tid":777533,"uid":127453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:48:39.000Z","msg":"外母嬲你地互射唔叫埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f63491253ecefd6976167c6a49fabf8b966c8d8","tid":777533,"uid":163937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:42:34.000Z","msg":"可能你外母鐘意咗你<br />\n嬲尻你屌佢個仔唔屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b63a502eb6adf44827d68115db037b36c0094b","tid":777533,"uid":106523,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:44:04.000Z","msg":"結婚就結婚<br